locator = splinter_strategy, str(random.random())
from mock import PropertyMock
visible_mock = PropertyMock(return_value=False)
page.driver.configure_mock(**{'find_by_{0}.return_value.first.visible'.
    format(splinter_strategy): visible_mock})
type(getattr(page.driver, 'find_by_{0}'.format(splinter_strategy)).
    return_value.first).visible = visible_mock
assert not page.is_element_displayed(*locator)
getattr(page.driver, 'find_by_{0}'.format(splinter_strategy)
    ).assert_called_once_with(locator[1])
visible_mock.assert_called_with()
